<div class="comment"><p>Here is another popular <a href="https://everythingfonts.com/font-face">Webfont Generator</a>. <br />
I use this often. Between fontsquirrel and everythingfonts generator the later is simplest you can get (one click) the former gives you lots of option if you are a pro.</p></div>

